Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:03.85,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Team RWBY, mission one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:06.36,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Redecorating complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:07.78,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.78,0:00:09.48,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,It looks really comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:15.50,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a bunk bed before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:18.99,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, our next mission is class!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:22.21,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,You're always so excited for everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:57.41,main,Peter,0000,0000,0000,,Beasts of destruction \Nand carnage—the Grimm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:02:01.26,main,Peter,0000,0000,0000,,While much of their nature remains a mystery,\Nwe have learned a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:05.64,main,Peter,0000,0000,0000,,Grimm are born and raised in the darkness, \Nwhere they learn to be very vigilant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:08.21,main,Peter,0000,0000,0000,,When Grimm die, they immediately\N return to dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:10.68,main,Peter,0000,0000,0000,,and they are thought to have no soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:15.27,main,Peter,0000,0000,0000,,It is the Huntsman's duty \Nto wield this knowledge in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:18.94,main,Peter,0000,0000,0000,,Do any of you wish to test your skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:21.29,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,How did they capture that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:28.33,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Go get 'em, Weiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.91,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Represent Team RWBY! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:32.41,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:33.41,main,Peter,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:47.14,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Its weak point is its belly! Go low!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:48.72,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Stop telling me what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:14.30,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,You did it! You did it, Weiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:16.87,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.40,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, Weiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:32.81,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you so mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:36.32,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.61,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Quit babbling like a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:42.83,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really so happy about being team leader\N when you barely did anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:45.68,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,I just want us to work \Ntogether as a team and—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:47.28,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Not a team led by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.86,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:55.66,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,Let Ruby handle it. If she doesn't deal \Nwith this herself, it'll keep happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.78,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,After studying and \Ntraining myself to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:05.01,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,I deserve better than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:09.89,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:11.44,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:16.89,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:21.41,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'm fit to be a leader, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:25.40,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, they're gonna tell me \NI don't even belong at Beacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:27.20,main,Ozpin,0000,0000,0000,,That remains to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:34.98,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Port.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:37.98,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,May I speak with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:43.65,main,Ozpin,0000,0000,0000,,I do not consider your appointment \Nas leader to be a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:48.86,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,But Weiss doesn't agree. \NShe says I haven't made any effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:52.55,main,Ozpin,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, nobody will follow a leader \Nthat doesn't do their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:57.56,main,Ozpin,0000,0000,0000,,Take some time and think about\Nhow you should carry out your responsibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:02.35,main,Peter,0000,0000,0000,,And you think making you\Nteam leader would solve everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:06.02,main,Peter,0000,0000,0000,,Your skills are exceptional, \Nbut your attitude is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.24,main,Peter,0000,0000,0000,,They cancel each other out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.07,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.66,main,Peter,0000,0000,0000,,My point exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:14.07,main,Peter,0000,0000,0000,,You've probably spent your whole \Nlife getting exactly what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:18.00,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't... true. At all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.93,main,Peter,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of throwing tantrums, \Ntry to become the best person,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:23.87,main,Peter,0000,0000,0000,,the best teammate you can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:28.38,main,Peter,0000,0000,0000,,You'll soon realize that it \Ndoesn't matter who the leader is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:33.24,main,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:36.08,main,Pyrrha,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Jaune!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:37.92,main,Nora,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:39.64,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down and keep your eyes on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:43.38,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Jaune! Team JNPR!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:47.15,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Am I too loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:52.40,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,No. Cheering needs to be loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:55.87,main,Glynda,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:06:00.12,main,Glynda,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, Jaune's Aura has been \Ngreatly reduced from taking damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:04.44,main,Glynda,0000,0000,0000,,You must choose a fighting style \Nthat fits within the limits of your Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:14.26,main,Pyrrha,0000,0000,0000,,Aura is present in all \Nliving things, except Grimm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:20.52,main,Pyrrha,0000,0000,0000,,See, you have to release the Aura \Nthat sleeps inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:28.08,main,Jaune,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:30.53,main,Jaune,0000,0000,0000,,But what is this good for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:34.11,main,Pyrrha,0000,0000,0000,,It is your strongest shield \Nand your most powerful weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:37.28,main,Pyrrha,0000,0000,0000,,As your Aura grows, your own \Nunique power will also awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:39.04,main,Pyrrha,0000,0000,0000,,That's your Semblance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:41.05,main,Pyrrha,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:43.54,main,Jaune,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:52.84,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,How was he able to enroll \Nwhen he didn't even know about Aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:57.38,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,But what's more important is that\N Pyrrha unquestioningly accepted
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:07:00.15,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,that useless Jaune as team leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:04.37,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you can score more points \Nby being a perfect teammate
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:07.60,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,and supporting a poor leader, \Nrather than becoming a leader yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.97,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.95,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.37,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I fell asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:26.75,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:31.97,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Cream and five sugars. \NJust how you like it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.55,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.26,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,I know you'll become a good leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:41.36,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:45.46,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to be the best teammate I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:46.96,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.15,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:54.50,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted a bunk bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:05.55,italics,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,This is more exhausting than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.49,main,Jaune,0000,0000,0000,,My own unique power...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:15.42,italics,Another Jaune,0000,0000,0000,,It'll never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:18.68,italics,Another Jaune,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, you've \Ngot no right to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.43,italics,Another Jaune,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:30.17,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Jaune, it's time for class. Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:32.18,main,Nora,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Did he catch a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:34.09,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,He must be tired from training.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:42.99,main,Pyrrha,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong with his Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:07.35,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,It's my target. We need to\Nbegin immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.16,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Shion Zaiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:27.24,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Nightmare Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:28.61,main,Pyrrha,0000,0000,0000,,What's a Nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:33.99,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,A type of Grimm that possesses humans \Nand grows by draining their Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.54,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,The possessed victim is trapped in their dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:39.27,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,as their body becomes\Na breeding ground for Grimm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.24,main,Nora,0000,0000,0000,,So we just have to kill the Grimm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:44.45,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, inside his dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:46.14,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Inside his dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:48.76,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,It's a task for his close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:53.09,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,If a stranger tries, \Nhis heart will reject them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:59.03,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,Are any of you willing to enter \Nhis dream to battle the Grimm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:01.65,main,Pyrrha,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely. We'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:28.49,main,Shield,0000,0000,0000,,For generations, males of the Arc Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:31.27,main,Shield,0000,0000,0000,,have been fated to become glorious warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.20,main,Sword,0000,0000,0000,,And then you showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:36.14,main,Sword,0000,0000,0000,,What a disappointment you are, Jaune.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:40.72,main,Armor,0000,0000,0000,,You incompetent, miserable coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:46.99,main,Jaune,0000,0000,0000,,No... I know I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:48.54,main,Jaune,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:54.51,main,Boy Jaune,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis, I'm scared. Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:00.11,main,Pyrrha,0000,0000,0000,,Jaune!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:01.63,main,Boy Jaune,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:08.59,main,Pyrrha,0000,0000,0000,,We've come to get you, Jaune.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:17.54,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.22,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find him safely?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:24.41,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. You must fight to set him free.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:29.10,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,They were able to find Jaune.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:31.54,main,Ozpin,0000,0000,0000,,That was quick. Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:34.53,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,The care they show for each other
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:36.80,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,is what makes them a good team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.06,main,Jaune,0000,0000,0000,,Pyrrha...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:16.98,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's your turn to be trapped, Nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:19.24,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,Stay in there, and turn back into a seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:27.81,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,A seed... It's like a plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:30.81,main,Glynda,0000,0000,0000,,Typically, Grimm take on a beast form.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:34.67,main,Glynda,0000,0000,0000,,But some Grimm are unique. \NKeep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:44.95,main,Jaune,0000,0000,0000,,I overslept! Is class—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.25,main,Jaune,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:53.46,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we caught it before it grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:56.38,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably because his Aura \Nis still undeveloped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:13:00.59,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,His Semblance hasn't awakened, \Nand his Aura in combat is below average.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.51,top,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're safe, Jaune.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:03.59,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,That proved fortunate for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:03.59,top,Jaune,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:06.97,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen someone benefit \Nfrom a weakness before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:10.92,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,I sensed other Nightmares \Nin the forest, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:14.08,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,The more sensitive or emotionally \Nconflicted you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:15.48,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,the more susceptible you become.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:19.57,main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell the students to remain diligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:22.04,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:24.88,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,If you're feeling down, \Ntalk to each other about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:26.29,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,You must be joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:28.56,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,You can't possibly expect \Na Grimm to possess me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:30.84,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm sure you'll be fine, Weiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:32.90,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly does seem unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:35.75,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,She's got her own thorns \Nto use for keeping Grimm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:38.17,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:41.85,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, since tomorrow's a day off, \Nshall we go into town?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:43.63,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,The festival is soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.37,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:49.25,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you liked festivals, Weiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:50.52,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,That's a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:56.90,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:57.52,main,Police Officer,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:14:01.49,main,Police Officer,0000,0000,0000,,Another robbery.\NThey took the Dust and left everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:04.98,main,Police Officer,0000,0000,0000,,Probably the White Fang up \Nto their old tricks. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:11.93,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,The White Fang again? What a bunch \Nof violent, crazed degenerates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:14.62,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,They're a collection of misguided Faunus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.83,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,They say they're going to wipe \Nhumanity off the face of the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:19.18,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,That's only a small minority!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:22.05,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,And we don't even know \Nif Faunus did this to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:24.01,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Blake's got a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:28.51,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,The Dust robbery I saw was done by humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.89,main,Sailor 1,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that Faunus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.93,main,Sailor 1,0000,0000,0000,,You no-good stowaway!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:36.73,main,Sailor 2,0000,0000,0000,,You trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:41.27,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,If I were trash, you'd already\N have collected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:43.61,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,My skills at stowing away are second to none.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.11,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,What a weird comeback.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.04,main,Sailor 2,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:05.80,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll capture that Faunus \Nand show you just how bad he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.38,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Weiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.41,main,Penny,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:18.72,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:22.18,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,I am fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:24.37,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,Are you? Can you get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:27.45,main,Penny,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I am wonderful. Thank you for asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:29.38,main,Penny,0000,0000,0000,,And-a upsy-daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.95,main,Penny,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Penny. \NIt is a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.69,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Very nice to meet you, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:37.71,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry, the vagabond will get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:39.58,main,Penny,0000,0000,0000,,What did you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:41.45,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:43.71,main,Penny,0000,0000,0000,,No. You.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:48.97,main,Penny,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just call me "friend"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:51.09,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.46,main,Penny,0000,0000,0000,,Grin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:55.79,main,Penny,0000,0000,0000,,How touching! I have made a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:57.60,main,Penny,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I came to Vale!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.23,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,What is with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:01.34,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but we're in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:03.28,main,Penny,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:08.08,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give up. He's just a stowaway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:10.49,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,He's a law-breaking scoundrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:13.53,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,If we let him go, he'll surely\N join the White Fang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:16.41,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong! This is why \Nyou're so ignorant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:20.12,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:22.70,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,You're being prejudiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.70,0:16:25.62,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,You treat all Faunus like criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:28.42,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,If he's a scoundrel, then so are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:31.22,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,It's an organization of pure evil \Nthat hates humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.76,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,How can you defend them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:35.12,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing as pure evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:38.22,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,People like you drove the Faunus into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.39,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't fight, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:47.78,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Have you attended any of the\Nfunerals of the people they killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:52.18,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the pain of the families \Nwhose loved ones were killed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:54.44,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,just for being Company board members?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:56.87,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how much \Nthey've made me suffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:17:00.25,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe we were just \Ntired of being pushed around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.29,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,"We"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:10.05,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Blake, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:20.45,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:25.31,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd look better without the bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.04,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find Blake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:31.80,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,No. She might not be at the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.75,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,We should just leave her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:35.40,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,She's our teammate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:37.55,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,You heard what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:39.87,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to treat\Nher like a criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:42.41,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check by the warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.14,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.85,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:51.95,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to hate her just for being\Na Faunus, then you really are a bigot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:55.86,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,I... Maybe I went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:57.10,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,But that organization is—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:59.69,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough about the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:07.98,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:11.82,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute. You were\Na member of the White Fang?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:15.07,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I was a member \Nfor most of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:19.67,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid creeps that use force to get whatever they want...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:21.45,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't seem like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:25.96,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,The White Fang was supposed to be\Na bridge between humans and the Faunus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:30.09,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,But they changed, so I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:34.07,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to dedicate my life \Nto something truly important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:37.72,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,So, have you told your friends any of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:41.52,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what's your plan now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:45.44,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,I want to find out who's \Nbehind these Dust robberies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:49.10,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,You know, someone was talking \Nabout it on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:52.80,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,A Schnee Company freighter \Nis bringing in a load of Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:54.10,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:56.16,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,To replace what was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:59.82,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,The thieves must feel like the goods \Nare being delivered straight to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:10.33,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Where could Blake be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:12.71,main,Penny,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the Faunus girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:15.17,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:21.54,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, how did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:23.49,main,Penny,0000,0000,0000,,Because of her cat ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:25.92,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Ears? Not a bow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:27.81,main,Penny,0000,0000,0000,,I saw her with it off, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.04,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.95,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care about her at all, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:39.25,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're only pretending \Nto be nice to my sister, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:42.68,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,Like making up that stuff \Nabout always wanting a bunk bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:46.33,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you say something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:49.17,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:53.48,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't become the leader, \Ncouldn't even get on Pyrrha's team,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:55.71,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,and now one of my teammates is a Faunus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:20:01.39,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is turning out the \Nway I imagined it. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:03.38,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,She's crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:07.60,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:11.36,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:13.35,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:16.12,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,You know I'm an expert stowaway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:33.13,main,Roman,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Take all of the cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:35.75,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,The White Fang!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.89,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,They're not supposed to work with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:40.53,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they changed their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:43.71,main,Sun,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:48.80,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:50.10,main,Penny,0000,0000,0000,,That was a gunshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.22,0:20:53.93,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,You spoil Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:58.11,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she's always showing off \Nher abilities to get praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:20:59.71,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:01.55,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:05.13,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,But why don't you stop bragging \Nabout being the perfect teammate,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:07.34,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,and actually think about \Nwhat it means to be a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:09.44,main,Police Officer,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Dust robbery! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:14.00,main,Roman,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! What is that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:28.21,main,Penny,0000,0000,0000,,Swoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:33.31,main,Penny,0000,0000,0000,,Battle complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.52,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:40.89,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby! Blake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:44.54,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:46.94,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Blake isn't in the White Fang anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.94,0:21:50.87,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,and she has cat ears under her bow. \NIsn't that cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:52.21,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:56.99,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss, I haven't been in the organization—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:21:59.59,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear any more \Nabout the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:03.22,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,But I have been thinking about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:07.72,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,I kept thinking, thinking, \Nthinking, and decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:12.98,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.98,0:22:15.10,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:19.26,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,Right. So, the next time \Nyou have a big problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.26,0:22:23.74,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,come and talk to your teammates,\Nnot some stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.30,0:22:35.54,main,Blake,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.10,0:22:38.60,main,Yang,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:41.35,main,Ruby,0000,0000,0000,,Team RWBY is back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:44.36,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,You're celebrating a little too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:54.22,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't lying about always wanting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:57.64,italics,Phantom Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,You've buried all your dreams \Nthat didn't come true,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:23:01.05,italics,Phantom Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,and it takes all your strength \Nto pretend not to care.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.05,0:23:05.72,italics,Phantom Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,The Faunus, the White Fang... \NYou will never be able to forgive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:31.88,main,Weiss,0000,0000,0000,,What... What is this... thing?
